data.description: Welcome to this lovely Cape Code style home in a GREAT neighborhood in Lima's West end! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath is in THE Perfect location; this property is situated within walking distance of the bus stop for both Shawnee Local Schools and Lima City Schools. The roof was completely redone in 2013 (full tear-off!)! This property boasts a 2 car PLUS garage!! Full basement that is partially finished. The Electric Range, Dishwasher, Frig will remain with this home. This is a great location right in the heart of Lima with easy access to just about everything - the many great local restaurants, shopping (grocery, home improvement and convenience stores) as well as parks and all the fun Lima has to offer. This one's got it all, it won't last long!
